Sony has announced that its Days of Play sale will return this year, offering savings on PlayStation hardware, games, and services. The sale will take place from 8-18 June 2018, and will include discounts on a new limited-edition Days of Play PS4 console. This 500GB console will be available while stocks last for R4,999 during the sale period. After 18 June, it will retail for R5,299. The PlayStation Store will also offer discounts on triple-A titles like Horizon Zero Dawn and God of War, in addition to hardware bundles like the PS VR starter pack. PlayStation’s Days of Play sale includes the following deals in South Africa: